abstract = {A relation for the variation of the energy gap (Eg) with temperature (T) in semiconductors is proposed. Eg ≐ E0 - αT2/(T+β) where α and β are constants. The equation satisfactorily represents the experimental data for diamond, Si, Ge, 6H-SiC, GaAs, InP and InAs.}
